{"tid":266972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"估國家? 淫蕩女教師和13歲男學生做愛 判刑3年","createTime":"2017-06-02T01:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T03:06:55.000Z","uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6b748fc36337a717712bc34e1affae5f906c2d","tid":266972,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:49:16.000Z","msg":"內地江蘇省一名30多歲的中學女教師，和班上的男學生發生性關係，被法院判刑3年。<br />\n《現代快報》報導，黃姓女教師在2013年，擔任王姓男學生的導師，黃女知道王男不足14歲的情況下，於2014年3月至8月間，多次在家中、賓館等地和他發生性行為。2人首次做愛時，是黃女幫他輔導功課的時候。<br />\n據了解，黃女失婚，和王男多次上床後，王男的家人調查他的微信，發現不尋常，加上成績下滑、經常不回家和夜歸等，向校方反映，事件才曝光。<br />\n當地法院審理後，認為黃女犯下猥褻兒童罪，判3年有期徒刑。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/other/%E6%B7%AB%E8%95%A9%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%92%8C13%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9A%E6%84%9B-%E5%88%A4%E5%88%913%E5%B9%B4/ar-BBBMvtf?li=%24filter%3d(%27_links.feed.href%27eq%27cms%2fapi%2famp%2ffeed%2fBByDoFZ%27or%27_links.feed.href%27eq%27cms%2fapi%2famp%2ffeed%2fBByzAho%27or%27_links.feed.href%27eq%27cms%2fapi%2famp%2ffeed%2fBByDtpR%27)and(%27%24type%27eq%27article%27or%27%24type%27eq%27slideshow%27or%27%24type%27eq%27video%27or%27%24type%27eq%27puzzle%27)%26%24orderby%3d%27displayPublishedDateTime%27+desc&amp;ocid=spartandhp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fother%2F%25E6%25B7%25AB%25E8%2595%25A9%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2592%258C13%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2584%259B-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%25913%25E5%25B9%25B4%2Far-BBBMvtf%3Fli%3D%2524filter%253d%28%2527_links.feed.href%2527eq%2527cms%252fapi%252famp%252ffeed%252fBByDoFZ%2527or%2527_links.feed.href%2527eq%2527cms%252fapi%252famp%252ffeed%252fBByzAho%2527or%2527_links.feed.href%2527eq%2527cms%252fapi%252famp%252ffeed%252fBByDtpR%2527%29and%28%2527%2524type%2527eq%2527article%2527or%2527%2524type%2527eq%2527slideshow%2527or%2527%2524type%2527eq%2527video%2527or%2527%2524type%2527eq%2527puzzle%252